89
00:06:13,519 --> 00:06:14,800
[Actually, I want to pursue you.]

90
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,079
[I wanted to tell you]

91
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,279
[when we first]

92
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,879
[met for dating.]

93
00:06:24,879 --> 00:06:26,560
[You approached me,]

94
00:06:26,759 --> 00:06:27,920
[protected me,]

95
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:30,040
[but pushed me away.]

96
00:06:31,439 --> 00:06:33,839
[How many secrets are you hiding?]

97
00:06:35,279 --> 00:06:37,199
The more you keep distance with me,

98
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:39,240
the more I want to get close to you.

99
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,319
Shen Shutu,

100
00:06:42,079 --> 00:06:44,240
I wish you safe.

101
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,279
You spent so much money

102
00:07:19,279 --> 00:07:20,879
and effort,

103
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,759
but you tell me that

104
00:07:22,759 --> 00:07:24,680
